          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1667322295050-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Scrunch the edges of the foil around the greens to form a tightly sealed parcel (or two!)</p><p>When the fishcakes have 12 min remaining, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the parcel[s] to the other side, then return it to the oven for a final 12 min until tender with a slight bite – these are your <strong>fragrant green beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
