            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>salmon & saag aloo-style fishcakes </strong>with the <strong>fragrant green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>coriander mayo</strong> all over and garnish with the <strong>reserved chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and<strong> coriander </strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
